GMRs. Therein, the majority of the best models base on an\nanisotropic point source approach. The residual variance of logarithmized PGA\nis significantly smaller than in previous models. We validate the estimations\nfor the event with the largest sample by empirical area functions. etc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 May 2012 18:50:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 21 Oct 2012 11:50:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 25 Oct 2012 14:54:28 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 29 May 2013 15:49:58 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sat, 13 Jul 2013 16:58:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
