ue of\n{\\epsilon}_g indicates that microscopic electron-electron interactions can\ncontribute significantly to graphene properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 May 2012 22:01:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-02"}
